links.description: This full-rimmed frame comes in a Brown Tortoiseshell finish that exudes confidence and style. The luxurious acetate finish means Claudia is both comfortable and durable, while the spring hinges ensure a comfortable fit on any face. Pick these up to add some understated style to your wardrobe.

This look is all Attitude, featuring an elegant ivory tortoise frame with slim metal arms in gold. The horn shape and standout metal hinges adds to its timeless style, complete with matching tortoise temple tips to top it all off. Perfect to wear in the office or out on the town.

Enter — Attitude. This Gray Tortoise Acetate aceate frame breaks new boundaries in both fashionable and practical eyewear design. Don't miss out on this style's deep-cut nose bridge, elegant Gold temple arms, and timeless cat eye lenses.

Enter — Attitude. This Black aceate frame breaks new boundaries in both fashionable and practical eyewear design. Don't miss out on this style's deep-cut nose bridge, elegant Gold temple arms, and timeless cat eye lenses.

Enter — Attitude. This Clear aceate frame breaks new boundaries in both fashionable and practical eyewear design. Don't miss out on this style's deep-cut nose bridge, elegant Gold temple arms, and timeless cat eye lenses.

Time for an Attitude check. This mixed-material frame is making itself seen in a new limited-edition summer color. The modern silhouette features lightweight acetate, a deep-cut nose bridge, and slim gold arms with flared acetate temple tips. Rosy and ready for summer, the petal pink face front adds a welcome pop of color.
Add a dash of European sophistication to your outfit with Yokote. The square lenses in matte grey and silver are as cool and fresh as a stroll along the Seine.
Set hearts racing with these Yokote eyeglasses. These full-rim lenses in deep matte burgundy will add the finishing touch to any outfit.
Look a million dollars in these Yokote eyeglasses. The square, full-rim lenses in black and silver will add a touch of cool sophistication to any outfit.

There’s only one look for those who like to stand out, and that would be Iconic. This bold aviator frame falls somewhere between retro and modern, with its mixed material design featuring acetate and metal. The slim silver arms balance the angular face front in black, while the tortoiseshell temple tips complete the look.

Make an Iconic fashion statement with a pair of striking aviator frames. Retro meets modern with this mixed material look that will be sure to turn heads — featuring an eye-catching acetate face front with a bold tortoise finish, and slim silver metal arms to balance the look. Complete with matching tortoiseshell temple tips.

That’s Amore! These too-cute rimless glasses will change your outlook with a little love, and a lot of style. This lightweight look features subtle temples in lustrous gold metal, always on trend tortoiseshell temple tips, and adjustable nose pads for a secure and comfortable fit you can’t help falling for.

Put a little love in your heart with Amore — a heart-shaped rimless look that’s not only super cute, it’s also super-functional. This lightweight style was made for all-day wear, featuring adjustable nose pads for a secure and custom fit, with silver metal accents and tortoiseshell temple tips to top it all off.

It’s easy to fall for Amore. These rimless heart-shaped lenses will add a little bit more love to any look. The vibrant red details stand out against the clear lenses, while the dark tortoiseshell temple tips add a touch of sophistication to this playful style. Plus, they offer adjustable nose pads for added comfort.
Take the first step with Movement in Rose Gold. This glamorous, larger than life metal frame simply oozes style.

Looking to stand out, while still being understated? This bright red wire frame, with its unique square shape and bold color, couldn’t be closer to just that. Vintage with a side of modern, Movement will perfectly punctuate any look with a pop of color. With adjustable nose pads for a comfortable fit.

Look no further than Movement, a striking metal frame, boasting an unconventional square silhouette. The milky white finish offers a blend of vintage charm and contemporary flair, effortlessly adding sophistication to any ensemble. Complete with adjustable nose pads for a custom fit.
Round out your look with these stylish acetate eyeglasses. This round matte black frame with metal temples is handsome and smart with a certain playful air.

Effortlessly showcase your unique style with Ernst, featuring timeless elegance and artistic allure. Meticulously crafted from durable bio-based acetate,* these stylish frames show off chic translucent brown finish, paired with a subtle cat-eye shape for a striking appearance. *Acetate having 61% bio-based carbon content representing the amount of plant-based carbon in the material compared to fossil-based carbon.

Express your distinct style effortlessly with Ernst, embodying timeless sophistication and artistic charm. Crafted from sturdy bio-based acetate,* these classic frames boast a tortoise pattern, coupled with a subtle cat-eye silhouette for a distinctive aesthetic that makes a lasting impression. *Acetate having 61% bio-based carbon content representing the amount of plant-based carbon in the material compared to fossil-based carbon.

The emerald green geometries of Carmel are nothing short of dazzling. Like the city by the sea these frames get their name from, there is nothing subtle about this eyewear. Easy on the eyes and heavy on glamour, these glasses are best worn by divas with big personalities.

Oversized and orange, Carmel brings a delicious color contrast to the blue skies and beaches of its namesake. Bold and brassy, these are the ultimate in boho statement frames. A perfect match with basic blacks or flowing white linens, it hardly matters– all eyes will be on these juicy eyeglasses.

Like its namesake, Carmel is bold, bohemian, and multidimensional. These chunky, oversized tortoise frames are gorgeously geometric and classically-colored. Luxe metal details and exposed metal temples strike the perfect balance between excess and restraint.

Carmel is calling, and don't you dare hang up! Delicious striped raspberry acetate meets gorgeous geometries and sleek metal details in these too-good-to-be-true frames. Gutsy and glamorous, these eyeglasses take us into full-on diva territory. Only scene-stealers need apply.

Our all-time best-selling frame, St Michel is here with a new look. The shiny rainbow finish gives this classic metal style a whole new persona, with bold colors surrounding the round lenses for a mix of retro and modern. Complete with adjustable nose pads for a custom fit, and tortoise temple tips for comfort.

Become a 21st-century saint of style with St Michel. The contrast between sleek, matte bronze metal and retro shaped lenses makes these full-rim eyeglasses uniquely trendy. The smooth, wireframe design is complemented by a thin nose bridge and tortoise temple tips to create a frame that gives an instant, edgy style boost.

The contrast between sleek metal and retro shaped lenses makes these full-rim eyeglasses uniquely trendy. The smooth, streamlined design is complemented by a fine nose bridge and tortoise temple tips to create a frame that gives an instant, edgy style boost. Holiday Limited Edition.

It's not your fault that your sense of style is heavenly: that's just your cross to bear. Sleek, trendy gunmetal frames with a classic high arching nose bridge make St Michel the standard bearer of both minimalist and retro vibes.

The contrast between sleek, matte gold metal and retro outsize shaped lenses makes these full-rim eyeglasses uniquely trendy. The smooth, streamlined design is complemented by a fine nose bridge and black temple tips to create a frame that gives an instant, edgy style boost.

Add a touch of eclectic sophistication to any occasion. Romy shows off a captivating blend of modern flair and vintage charm. Bold yet subtle, these square frames in translucent light green acetate are perfect for embracing both bold statements and understated elegance.

Embrace that sophisticated look coveted by all with this pair of luxe and chic tortoise eyeglasses. Romy??s full-rim square lens design and acetate build mean you can be effortlessly fashionable and forever on trend. Timeless design and superior craftsmanship make these specs ideal for the everyday fashionista.

Embrace that sophisticated look coveted by all with this pair of luxe and chic black eyeglasses. Romy??s full-rim square lens design and acetate build mean you can be effortlessly fashionable and forever on trend. Timeless design and superior craftsmanship make these specs ideal for the everyday fashionista.

You can get much more sophisticated than Romy — a square frame with generous lenses and beyond chic style. The boldly patterned ivory tortoise elevates this eyewear for that always-on-trend look that’s coveted by all. Pairs just as well with a LBD as it does a simple t-shirt and jeans.

Full-rim and full of style, this look was made for the everyday eyeglass wearer with an eye for fashion. Romy makes a classic square frame chic with it’s chunky acetate construction and deep burgundy color. The timeless silhouette offers a look that will last, with double stud rivets to complete the look.

Bold and stylish, this full-rim frame is designed for the everyday eyeglass wearer who appreciates fashion. Romy elevates the classic square shape with its chunky acetate build and rich orange hue. The timeless silhouette is complemented by double stud rivets, adding a touch of refinement that ensures this look stands the test of time.

This bold browline style frame is perfectly complemented by the warm Tortoiseshell finish. The full-sized lenses and decorative hinge studs help this classy frame to stand out even further. Coexist is great for anyone looking for a modern twist on a classic style of frame.

Look sharp with these black and silver eyeglasses. This browline style frame comes in a glossy black acetate and silver metal accents. The classic retro style, square shaped lenses, and single stud accents create a strong look for both men and women.

Can you hear that? It’s this new limited-edition summer color calling to you. We absolutely amore Amity, a modern mixed-material frame, featuring a translucent plastic face front in a friendly orange hue. The exposed metal arms and round lenses exude femininity for a look that’s fit for any face, regardless of shape or size.

Bold translucent plastic meets sleek metal details to make Amity, a mixed-material frame in an outgoing evergreen hue. The round lenses showcase an ever-so feminine style, while the exposed metal arms are a welcome, eye-catching addition. This versatile eyewear can be paired with just about anything, for a look that can suit anyone.

Amity's full-rimmed frame and sleek round lenses represents decades of femme-forward eyewear fashion. In Clear Purple, this crystal-like frame is an excellent fit for any face shape — regardless of size.

Amity's full-rimmed frame and sleek round lenses represents decades of femme-forward eyewear fashion. In Clear Pink, this crystal-like frame is an excellent fit for any face shape — regardless of size.

Amity's full-rimmed frame and sleek round lenses represents decades of femme-forward eyewear fashion. In Clear Blue, this crystal-like frame is an excellent fit for any face shape — regardless of size.

A refined blend of ivory tortoiseshell acetate and sleek metal makes this round frame effortlessly sophisticated. Quill’s distinct curves and striking color palette make it an essential for the modern style enthusiast.
In Tortoiseshell, Quill's elegant curves and colors give it an unmistakable flourish. This marriage of metal and acetate is a must-have for any urban fashion fan.
In vogue Red, Quill's sensual silhouette give it a passionate but classy aura. This masterful combination of metal and lightweight acetate make it a must-have for the urban scene and beyond.

Tower is a classic square frame made modern with crystal clear acetate. This wear-with-anything look will feel right at home with any wardrobe, perfect for those looking for a practical pair of specs with no shortage of style. Designed with spring hinges for extra comfort so you can wear them all day, every day.

Studious and serious or fun and flirty, Tower in Tortoise pulls off both looks at the same time. Women and men alike can appreciate the classic style with modern appeal. The square lens shape and full-rim frame make a statement anywhere – what they say is up to you.

Classic, timeless and a little bit rebellious, the versatile Tower feels right at home at staff meetings or rock concerts. The unique Green Tortoiseshell adds a vintage flair while projecting a distinctively modern style. Handcrafted from acetate, these functional full-rim frames with flexible spring hinges work well for women or men.

Tower in Gray can complete your fierce formal look or accentuate a casually cool vibe. This distinctive full-rim frame made from durable acetate features spring hinges for comfort and reliability. Sharp, smooth and sophisticated, they’ll make the perfect accessory to complement your classic-modern style.

You’ll radiate with self-confidence and exude stylishness in the super chic and fashion-forward Tower. The vivid Blood Orange finish perfectly complements the classic full-rim frame shape for a look that’s both daring and practical. They are crafted from acetate with spring hinges for durable flexibility and versatility to wear everywhere.

This rimless metal frame features a bronze finish and perfectly round lenses. The slender metal arms are completed with tortoise arm tips and spring hinges, making this frame a simple yet fashionable choice.

These black eyeglasses definitely have a classic vintage feel. This rimless metal frame features a glossy black finish and perfectly round lenses. The slender metal arms are completed with plastic arm tips, making this look demur and simple. Spring hinges add flexibility and comfort.

This rimless metal frame features a bronze finish and perfectly round lenses. The slender metal arms are completed with tortoise arm tips and spring hinges, making this frame a simple yet fashionable choice.

Hubris features a classic full-rimmed trapezoid shape and a sophisticated Clear Copper finish. The lightweight plastic construction of Hubris means they are extra comfortable while extra features like the oval hinge studs add an eyecatching touch to this attractive frame.

Some might fault you for being a little overconfident, but Hubris makes it hard not to be. Timeless round frames are elevated to a stratospheric level of style in black and white floral pattern. It's hard to pull off a look so classic and yet so fresh, but somehow you manage.

When iconic round frames with a refined traditional style join forces with crystal-clear blue acetate, the result is bound to put a little swagger in your step. Before you get carried away with the charm Hubris exudes, take a moment to appreciate the details: a wide keyhole bridge and oval accent studs.

The fact that you look too cool for school isn't your fault, you can blame it on Hubris. In frosted crystal, these frames are so fresh that they leave every other style struggling to catch up. Day or night, work or play, wherever you go, your glasses will make the scene.

Fame comes in all sorts of different ways. Some of those being Pink Golden. This playfully classy aviator style packs more character than you could ever want in an accessory. With its unique double nose bridge, slim temple arms, and adjustable nose pads, you can bet that this will be your next favorite.

Fame is an instant eyecatcher. In Silver, this characteristic style's striking silhouette makes it a potent way to update any look from drab to lively. A classy double nose bridge and adjustable nose pads make it a frame fit for any occasion.

Larger than life and just as fashionable. For an aviator style with unrivaled class, look no further than Fame in Black. This unique style's urban double nose bridge, unique temple arms, and adjustable nose pads let it sit nicely on the cutting edge of style.

There’s something about Aroma that we just can't get enough of… Now in a limited-edition color, this lightweight acetate frame features a splash of sea green for a look that’s ready for summer. The slim arms add a touch of subtlety to these full-rim cat-eye specs, while spring hinges complete the look with added comfort.

In classy Raspberry acetate comes Aroma, our latest in cat eye fashion. This lightweight frame's full-rimmed design, slimmed down temple arms, and subtle curves make it a must-have for any style fan. Spring hinges allow for easy and comfortable wear.

An all-around favorite, Aroma is now available in an additional limited-edition summer color. This full-rim cat-eye frame features lightweight acetate with a pop of peachy pink, and slim arms for an airy look that's as subtle as it is stylish. Plus spring hinges for extra comfort that you can count on.

Make room for this oversized mixed-material frame — featuring slim black acetate, slightly tapered metal arms, and tortoiseshell temple tips for contrast. Corey’s softly curved square lenses and generous silhouette add a subtle vintage charm, with a certain comfort from the addition of spring hinges (so you can wear this look all day, every day).

Turn heads and set trends with Corey in tortoise — a standout square frame, featuring a mixed-material construction of acetate and metal. The slim silver arms compliment the patterned face front and temple tips for a striking look, with a certain comfort that can only be possible with spring hinges.

Meet Corey — a mixed-material frame with softly curved square lenses and subtle vintage charm. The full-rim face front features translucent brown acetate, met with slim metal arms and tortoiseshell temple tips to top it all off. This stylish look was designed with spring hinges for added comfort and wearability.

There’s no mixed emotions when it comes to this mixed-material square frame. Corey makes it easy to fall for its vintage charm — all it takes is one look at the mustard yellow face front, slim metal arms, and tortoiseshell temple tips. Complete with spring hinges for added comfort and wearability.

Answer London's call with these indulgent cognac eyeglasses. This intellectual frame is hand crafted from a premium acetate in a fierce translucent amber finish. Dainty double stud accents, classic keyhole nose bridge, and high quality construction create an ultimately timeless piece that is both art and fashion.

Dainty double stud accents, classic keyhole nose bridge, and high quality construction create an ultimately timeless piece that is both art and fashion.

Dainty double stud accents, classic keyhole nose bridge, and high quality construction create an ultimately timeless piece that is both art and fashion.

Dainty double stud accents, classic keyhole nose bridge, and high quality construction create an ultimately timeless piece that is both art and fashion.

Go bold in Black with these uber-chic unisex frames. Tower expresses your independence and uncompromising sensibility in fashionable and functional black acetate. With spring hinges and enduring classic style, they’re sure to be a go-to accessory to your ensemble for years to come.
Think outside the box with these Sergi sunglasses. This broad-temples black acetate and wood texture frame is a quirky, winning combination.
